%F A047695 a(n) = sqrt(A000125(A047694(n))), where sqrt = A000194 or A000196. - _M. F. Hasler_, Jun 22 2024
%e A047695 For y = 8, we have 8^2 = 64 = 1 + 7 + 21 + 35 = Sum_{k=0..3} C(x, k) for x = 7.
